iprange
------------------------------------------
Manage IP ranges

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.7-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  help2man-1.49.3-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/firehol/iprange

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/firehol/iprange/archive/refs/tags/v2.0.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack iprange-2.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./iprange-2.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/iprange-2.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/iprange-2.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(iprange)
  /usr/bin/iprange.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/iprange.README
  /usr/share/doc/iprange/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/iprange/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/iprange/README.md
  /usr/share/man/man1/iprange.1.gz

------------------

